Arsenal beat Liverpool 4-1 in the Premier League at the Emirates Stadium on Saturday . 
  Hector Bellerin gave the Gunners the lead after 37 minutes . 
  Mesut Ozil and Alexis Sanchez made it 3-0 in the first half . 
  Olivier Giroud scored a late fourth to move Arsenal up to second in the table . 
  Arsene Wenger believes something is finally happening at Arsenal . 
 